{"tid":2035481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"破天荒回應郭偉健指兇徒「情操高尚」  馬道立：法官判詞加政見損法治","createTime":"2020-05-26T02:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T11:58:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1ca630b451bdc3efcd8a44303a60b2360c8e82","tid":2035481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:53:19.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/HYTGYNA4DKFDRGSDAHA2MU3HBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FHYTGYNA4DKFDRGSDAHA2MU3HBA%2F&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=a3a406ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FHYTGYNA4DKFDRGSDAHA2MU3HBA%2F&h=e827bd2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/HYTGYNA4DKFDRGSDAHA2MU3HBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n破天荒回應郭偉健指兇徒「情操高尚」 <br />\n馬道立：法官判詞加政見損法治<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【司法爭議】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】區域法院法官郭偉健上月判處將軍澳連儂牆斬人案時，大篇幅批評反修例示威，更讚揚斬傷三人的男被告「情操高尚」，引起激烈迴響，事後郭官被安排暫不處理反修例案件。終審法院首席法官馬道立昨發聲明回應，指郭官對受爭議的政治議題發表不必要的政見，予人偏頗觀感。聲明強調若司法人員發表不必要或不適當的政見，會削弱公眾對法庭的信心。<br />\n<br />\n記者：勞東來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200526/large/1590424003_6262.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200526%2Flarge%2F1590424003_6262.gif&h=db0dcf38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬道立罕有發聲明回應，冀挽回司法機構形象。易仰民攝<br />\n<br />\n馬道立昨日傍晚離開終審法院時，。。。。。。。。。。免令外界感覺法官判案時有偏頗。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：女傷者冀日後審訊引以為鑑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑：須力挽公眾信心<br />\n<br />\n資深大律師梁家傑直言執業30多年從未見過這樣發聲明。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構昨發表法官馬道立聲明時，。。。。。。。。。。。不可使人有理由覺得偏頗。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，。。。。。。。。。。。。不能超過合理所需。<br />\n<br />\n馬官指若偏離這些原則，。。。。。。。。。。。。及其審理與個人政治立場可能有關的案件的公信力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200526/large/1590424002_ad4d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200526%2Flarge%2F1590424002_ad4d.gif&h=5eabfad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將軍澳連儂牆斬人案，男導遊洪震斬傷兩女一男，26歲女記者一度命危。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭官暫禁審類似政治案件<br />\n<br />\n馬官透露已與郭官傾談，。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。郭官暫時不應審理任何涉及類似政治背景的案件。<br />\n<br />\n案發於去年8月20日，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n郭官雖自言「這次判刑與評論這次運動無關」，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n判詞成為新聞焦點，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎和葛珮帆回應。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"84192cc7fa95ded61082467adcded1208381bcf8","tid":2035481,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"國安法通過之後馬道立要坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ac2678b40506bb722f0e68084926e785028c60","tid":2035481,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"唔判都判咗，你係咪幫佢平反同比訟費先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939cd226cc80b82dbc594e9825edc12d2f08cf2d","tid":2035481,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:56:57.000Z","msg":"已經唔係講唔講野既問題<br />\n斬人都情操高尚<br />\n係人格都出現問題"},{"pid":"209aa97ba927c9f96c0ceee3d43325cbebc01ecd","tid":2035481,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"訓斥完就唔使負責任"},{"pid":"0479ed5805a053fb8fbb4bf57b966dbfca258724","tid":2035481,"uid":277925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"問題係法官錯判係無後果"},{"pid":"13a6eed6427fc1da17461702371a1064ff2e48ba","tid":2035481,"uid":61018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"維持原判 但出嚟講唔適當 會改進<br />\n即係點"},{"pid":"edd252facaf5272e8fc99a6e30c355f25afa3bcd","tid":2035481,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"我印象中都唔係第一次<br />\n有其他官講過<br />\n而家先黎出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm